text:
Before you come back home,
make sure to contact me, okay?!

I won't serve a master
who can't take care of things.

Amana, great job on the shoot.
The client seemed really pleased too.

That's wonderful!
Seems like it'll be a promotional hit with impact!

By the way, Producer-san, is he usually normal
or a bit strict? Which do you prefer?

Hmm... It's hard to say, but
I think I prefer him a bit strict.

I see... That's how it is, huh...
...Yeah...
